Description West Bay Oaks Mobile Home And Rv Park is an age-restricted (55+) manufactured home community located in 1610 W Bay Dr, Largo, FL 33770. West Bay Oaks Mobile Home And Rv Park is a land-lease community and has a total of 99 home sites. Home site lot rent ranges from $475 - $625 per month and includes the following: Trash pickup Water Sewer The streets in the community are paved, and are of an average street width. The water in the community is sourced from the well and the sewer system is septic. Parking is off-street The community has 0 parking spaces available for RVs. Managed on-site by West Bay Oaks. West Bay Oaks Mobile Home And Rv Park is an affordable housing choice for active, friendly, age-qualified living. This well-maintained retirement community has easy access to local recreation, shopping and entertainment. Log In transforming Lives West Bay Welcome to WEST BAY RI Our mission is to provide innovative, person-centered supports to people with intellectual and developmental disabilities in ways that promote community inclusion, personal power, self-expression and life fulfillment. Learn more about our Mission & Values . Supporting individuals with intellectual & developmental disabilities across Rhode Island since 1981. Donate Help Support Our Mission You can change people's lives by making a donation Featured Services Customized Employment & Day Services ​ West Bay is committed to providing individuals with intellectual and developmental disabilities with the tools and resources needed to seek and secure gainful employment. We believe every person has distinct talents and strengths, as well as an inherent right to full inclusion in the workplace. Shared Living (SLA) West Bay offers SLA as an opportunity for individuals with intellectual and developmental disabilities to live in private homes with dedicated contractors who support people with their personal growth and development. Supported Living In order to foster growth, maintain an individual’s independence and encourage community inclusion, West Bay offers custom-designed services to those with an established range of life skills. Residential Services West Bay offers a variety of innovative, person-centered residential living options to support people with intellectual and developmental disabilities in their daily lives. Presently, we operate over 30 individualized Residential Supports across Rhode Island.
